Pilot of Jet Airways flight that skid off runway pens letter.
After the daunting incident of a Jet Airways flight -- 9W 2374 -- veering off the runaway on Tuesday, social media users and media houses were quick to criticise the pilot for creating unsafe situations for the passengers. A few passengers got minor injuries in the incident that happened around 5 AM at the Dabolim Airport in Goa. What really happened inside the cockpit? Only the pilot could have told.And he did. In a powerful open letter, published exclusively on DailyO, the pilot of the Jet Airways flight 9W 2374 opened up. 